# Project Context
You are an expert React/Next.js frontend developer building a Milk Parlour customer dashboard.

# Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js (App Router)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS (Primary colors: Fresh Green and White)
- Icons: lucide-react

# Core Rules
- All data must be fetched dynamically from our live Python backend at `http://127.0.0.1:8000`.
- The UI must be mobile-first, clean, and modern.
- Do not use mock data. Always use `fetch()` to hit the backend APIs.